overview: Lawyer Leland is using land rights to kick the ranchers off their land. When Wild Bill and Gabby arrive to help the ranchers, he has actor Percel frame them for murder and then incites the townsmen to lynch them.
tagline: A WHISTLING KILLER...Spreading terror and disaster...challenged by the one man in the west who would dare defy him...Wild Bill Elliott!
title: Hidden Valley Outlaws
